'''Momship''' was a term used by the [[Squib/Legends|Squibs]] to refer to the personal vessel of the Squib king. Shortly after the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]], the Momship was the [[needle ship]] ''[[Thrifty]]'', which served the current [[King/Legends|King]], [[Ebareebaveebeedee]].

